## 9. Model Evaluation

### For Regression

| Metric | Formula | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| **MSE** | $\frac{1}{n}\sum(y_i - \hat{y}_i)^2$ | Penalises large errors |
| **RMSE** | $\sqrt{\text{MSE}}$ | Same units as $y$ |
| **MAE** | $\frac{1}{n}\sum\|y_i - \hat{y}_i\|$ | Robust to outliers |
| **R²** | $1 - \frac{\text{RSS}}{\text{TSS}}$ | Proportion of variance explained |
| **Adjusted R²** | $1 - (1-R^2)\frac{n-1}{n-p-1}$ | Penalises extra features |

Where $\text{TSS} = \sum_i (y_i - \bar{y})^2$.

### For Classification (Logistic Regression)

| Metric | Formula |
|---|---|
| **Accuracy** | $\frac{TP + TN}{TP + TN + FP + FN}$ |
| **Precision** | $\frac{TP}{TP + FP}$ |
| **Recall** | $\frac{TP}{TP + FN}$ |
| **F1 Score** | $\frac{2 \cdot \text{Precision} \cdot \text{Recall}}{\text{Precision} + \text{Recall}}$ |
| **AUC-ROC** | Area under the ROC curve |

