| Model | Penalty | Sparse Solution | Closed Form | Best Use Case |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **OLS** | None | ❌ | ✅ | Low-dim, well-behaved data |
| **Ridge** | $\lambda\|\boldsymbol{\beta}\|_2^2$ | ❌ | ✅ | Multicollinearity, many features |
| **Lasso** | $\lambda\|\boldsymbol{\beta}\|_1$ | ✅ | ❌ | Feature selection |
| **Elastic Net** | $\lambda_1\|\cdot\|_1 + \lambda_2\|\cdot\|_2^2$ | ✅ | ❌ | Correlated features + selection |
| **Logistic Reg.** | Optional | Optional | ❌ | Binary / multiclass classification |

