## Quick Reference — Key Equations

$$\underbrace{\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}} = (\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{X})^{-1}\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{y}}_{\text{OLS}} \qquad \underbrace{\hat{\boldsymbol{\beta}} = (\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{X} + \lambda\mathbf{I})^{-1}\mathbf{X}^\top\mathbf{y}}_{\text{Ridge}}$$

$$\underbrace{R^2 = 1 - \frac{\text{RSS}}{\text{TSS}}}_{\text{Goodness of Fit}} \qquad \underbrace{\hat{p} = \frac{1}{1+e^{-\boldsymbol{\beta}^\top\mathbf{x}}}}_{\text{Logistic Output}}$$

